original: Yeah, right!! Don't come to me with your feeble insecurities and petty neuroses. I will laugh in your face and crack open a low carb beer and a high protein snack. I'm a real man.
translated: 没错！！！别带着你那软弱不安和神经质来找我。我会喝着低碳啤酒，吃着高蛋白零食当面嘲笑你。我是纯爷们。

original: I don't want to talk about feelings and emotion. Power ballads get no play. I'm talking seriously misogynistic hip hop, I'm talking lap dancers. I'm talking blood sports and kung fu movies. Don't pay a therapist thousands of dollars to dredge up the painful events of your miserable past. Spend it on a fat spoiler and a night on the town with Brucie instead!!
translated: 我不想谈情感。强力谣曲屁用没有。我要的是歧视女性的嘻哈，要的是脱衣舞女。我要的是血腥运动和功夫电影。别花几千美元去找心理医生了，他只会翻你过去的悲痛历史。把钱花在宽大的扰流板上，夜里和Brucie一起进城浪！！

original: Forget about the past - this is your future. Grab it by the balls until it winces in pain. I don't care if you were beaten as a child. I don't want to hear about your desperation, loneliness, drunk uncle, rage and fear. I just want to know that you're ready to step up to the plate and get PUMPED!! WIN! WIN! WIN!
translated: 忘掉过去，这是你的未来。掐住它的蛋蛋，直到它疼得缩成一团。我不关心你小时候是不是被打过。我不想了解你的绝望、孤独、喝醉的叔叔、愤怒、恐惧。我只想知道你已经准备好嗨起来了！！耶！耶！耶！
